      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS timing. This unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-variable differential lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. While the aesthetics show honest patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including recent valve clearance adjustments and rod bearing service\u2014are current, ensuring optimal compression and thermal efficiency for the next enthusiast owner.",
