    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a 2018 Executive Sport Sedan in Mineral Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been thoughtfully maintained and presents a professional image. The exterior paint holds a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone peppering on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch near the fuel door. The 19-inch alloy wheels are wrapped in high-performance tires with approximately 65% tread life remaining; note that the front right wheel has a two-inch area of light curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a non-smoker environment featuring Oyster Dakota leather. The seats remain firm and supportive, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the heated steering wheel to the heads-up display and dual-zone climate control, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust. It comes with a documented service history, including a recent cooling system inspection and an oil change performed within the last 500 miles. The brakes are responsive with plenty of pad life left. This is a solid, reliable luxury vehicle that balances performance with everyday utility, showing only the honest wear expected of a car that has been driven and cared for properly.",
      "price": 34500.0,
